<h1>Enhancements:</h1>
<table border=0 cellpadding="6" cellspacing="0"><tr><td>
<LI>Converted to C++
<LI>Better memory usage
<LI>Faster
<LI>Handles larger pedigrees
<LI>Handles more markers
</td></tr></table>

<h1>Improvements in the pipeline</h1>
<table border=0 cellpadding="6" cellspacing="0"><tr><td>
<LI>Parallelisation for use on multi-cpu machines
<LI>New map building algorithm for use with large data sets
<LI>Better pedigree handling
</td></tr></table>
</div>

